  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The migration and refugee crises have remained a key challenge for the EU and have led to the setting up of a number of dedicated funding mechanisms such as the EU Trust Fund for Africa (to which Ireland made its last contribution in 2020) and the EU Turkey Refugee Facility, as elements of the EU&#x2019;s response. Ireland&apos;s support to the EU Trust Fund for Colombia is also drawn from this budget line.</narrative>
